It is a land around the azure water lakes, hemmed in by the Aravali Hills.
Founded by Maharan Udai singh, it was the capital city of the Rajput state, Mewar.
Udaipur is popular destination for organising various national and international cultural events.
Udaipur has a rich cultural heritage. Ghoomar, Kalbeila, Bhavai and Kachchhi Ghodi are various popular dance forms here.


